### Binary Distribution Requirements

When distributing compiled binaries:
* Include LICENSE file in distribution package
* Include NOTICE file with copyright information
* Provide link to source code repository
* Document any modifications or customizations
* Include trademark usage disclaimer

### Cloud/SaaS Distribution

When offering as a cloud service:
* Comply with all license terms
* Provide attribution in application footer or about page
* Maintain audit trail of modifications
* Ensure end-users can access license information

